title: Mindmap
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

A mindmap radiates outward from a single root. Use it for brainstorming, topic decomposition, and hierarchical thinking. ''New in Mermaid 9.4.''

---

!! Basic example

```
mindmap
  root((Mindmap))
    Origins
      Tony Buzan
      Ancient concept
    Uses
      Brainstorming
      Note-taking
      Planning
    Tools
      Paper
      Software
```

